Metric: Gross Merchandise Revenue
Description: Total gross revenue from all completed e-commerce orders before returns and chargebacks. Includes product subtotals, shipping, and taxes collected. Reported in the store's base currency (USD).
Owner: ecommerce-analytics
Tags: revenue, gmv, ecommerce, finance

Source: orders, invoices

Given the order status is "completed"
  And the invoice status is "finalized"
  And the order was placed within the reporting period
  And the currency has been normalized to USD

When we calculate
  Then sum the net amount from all qualifying order invoices
  And include tax collected
  And exclude orders still in "pending" or "canceled" status

The result is "Gross Merchandise Revenue"

Trust:
  Freshness must be less than 2 hours
  Null rate on net_amount must be less than 0%
  Null rate on currency must be less than 0%
  Null rate on status must be less than 0%
  Row count of orders must not drop more than 20% day over day
  Value must be between 100 and 50000000
  Value must not change more than 50% month over month
